Virginia Senate Live Session Video Stream


To watch a meeting, click on View Event, beside the meeting you would like to watch.

Citizens may testify virtually for standing committee meetings.
Registration for virtual testimony will open one half hour prior to each meeting.
At that time, a link to register for virtual testimony will appear in this box.
